    {
      "id": "port-projection-test-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Port Projection Test",
      "position": {
        "x": -120,
        "y": -140
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Port Projection Test\n\nUse this graph to verify the first declared-port slice.\n\nExpected behavior:\n\n- explicit `ports[]` declarations win\n- legacy `inputs[]` / `outputs[]` still project to the node boundary\n- nodes with no declarations still get the fallback `root` handle\n- explicit port ids should match edge endpoints",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
